            <ul style="margin-top: 10px; columns: 2; column-gap: 2.5rem;">
                <li>✔ Fully scripted / automated build</li>
                <li>✔ Hosted build platform (not local)</li>
                <li>✔ Ephemeral, isolated environment</li>
                <li>✔ No external influence beyond inputs</li>
                <li>✔ Signed provenance (non‑forgeable)</li>
                <li>✔ Secrets inaccessible to build steps</li>
                <li>✔ Cryptographic digest of artifact</li>
                <li>✔ Build metadata included</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- The workflow file you referenced -->
        <h2>📄 generator-generic-ossf-slsa3-publish.yml</h2>
        <div class="yaml-filename">.github/workflows/generator-generic-ossf-slsa3-publish.yml</div>
        <p>This reusable workflow from the <a href="https://github.com/slsa-framework/slsa-github-generator" target="_blank">SLSA GitHub Generator</a> builds a generic artifact and generates SLSA Level 3 provenance. Below is the canonical content (simplified for clarity). <a href="https://github.com/slsa-framework/slsa-github-generator/blob/main/.github/workflows/generator-generic-ossf-slsa3-publish.yml" target="_blank">🔗 View original on GitHub</a></p>
        <pre># generator-generic-ossf-slsa3-publish.yml
# Reusable workflow for SLSA Level 3 provenance (generic artifact)

on:
  workflow_call:
    inputs:
      artifact-path:
        description: 'Path to the artifact(s)'
        required: true
        type: string
      provenance-name:
        description: 'Provenance file name'
        required: false
        type: string
        default: 'provenance.intoto.jsonl'

jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - run: |                     # user-defined build
          mkdir -p $(dirname "${{ inputs.artifact-path }}")
          touch "${{ inputs.artifact-path }}"
      - uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
        with:
          name: artifact-for-provenance
          path: ${{ inputs.artifact-path }}

  provenance:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    needs: build
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - uses: actions/download-artifact@v4
        with:
          name: artifact-for-provenance
      - uses: slsa-framework/slsa-github-generator/actions/generator@v1.7.0
        id: generate
        with:
          artifact-path: ${{ inputs.artifact-path }}
          provenance-name: ${{ inputs.provenance-name }}
      - uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
        with:
          name: ${{ inputs.provenance-name }}
          path: ${{ steps.generate.outputs.provenance-path }}</pre>

